@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_cvknnp(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = v1
    tmp = wp.sin((wp.cos(v2 + 0.65) + (v1 + 0.49 / v0 + 0.03)))
    v2 = tmp
    v2 = (v0 + wp.exp(wp.abs(v2 + 0.89)))
    tmp = (wp.cos(wp.sin(v1 + 0.35)) / v0)
    tmp = (wp.exp((v0 + 0.37 - tmp + 0.54)) / v0)
    data[tid] = v0
